column2: SELECT p.objID, c.name, c.ra, c.dec FROM                      (CREATE TABLE #TEMP                     (                     NAME VARCHAR NOTNULL,                     RA REAL NOTNULL,                     DEC REAL NOTNULL                     )                     INSERT INTO #TEMP                       VALUES (UGC1#,#,#),(UGC0#,#,#),(UGC0#,#,#))                      AS c                 CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(c.ra, c.dec, #) AS near                 INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary AS p ON p.objID=near.objID                 INNER JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objID=p.objID
